                     <interp inst="t18431127-182-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 wooden bowl, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 6 shillings, 10 sixpences, and 8 groats; the property of <persName id="t18431127-name-977" type="victimName">
